04:39.000 --> 04:44.320
Huh? No, it's not hard to
change a tire.

04:47.500 --> 04:49.500
Hmm? It's strange.

04:49.900 --> 04:54.070
You told him you called the tow truck but the guy wants to check your tire.

04:54.250 --> 04:55.720
Wait, wait.

04:56.600 --> 04:58.200
What's the status?

05:01.200 --> 05:02.380
Okay.

05:02.810 --> 05:04.880
Hello? Joo-yeon, I think I should head out now.

05:07.260 --> 05:09.850
