05:57.100 --> 06:01.320
Ha...I'm sorry, I couldn't be with you for your birthday.

06:01.800 --> 06:04.470
Okay. I'll be there soon.

06:04.850 --> 06:06.350
Um.

06:17.350 --> 06:19.740
