11:56.300 --> 11:59.330
Spare my life, please.

14:44.210 --> 14:47.250
Dong-soo! Dong-soo!

14:48.200 --> 14:49.050
What?

14:49.060 --> 14:51.690
Come over here! Hurry Up!

15:42.500 --> 15:45.530
Detective! Why did you come out here?

15:45.560 --> 15:49.830
