24:31.470 --> 24:32.670
Isn't it marvelous?

24:37.040 --> 24:39.080
Good job.

24:39.220 --> 24:40.420
Thank you.

24:40.640 --> 24:42.870
You're welcome.

24:48.530 --> 24:49.430
Aren't you going in?

24:49.570 --> 24:50.220
Yes?

24:51.140 --> 24:53.340
