40:18.190 --> 40:19.710
Are you Sang-hoon?

40:26.480 --> 40:28.410
Do you know where your father lives now?

40:31.870 --> 40:37.370
Shit. Why do you ask?

44:05.470 --> 44:07.870
You guys don't go anywhere but home now, alright?

44:07.990 --> 44:08.950
Yes.

44:13.050 --> 44:15.290
Driver, please don't let them out anywhere else.

44:15.460 --> 44:16.090
Yeah.

44:16.410 --> 44:17.370
Thank you.

45:02.970 --> 45:04.170
Who are you?

45:04.300 --> 45:05.240
Is Jang Gyeong-chul here?

45:06.080 --> 45:07.000
Why do you ask that?

45:07.120 --> 45:08.860
