46:50.600 --> 46:51.250
Friend? Who?

46:51.390 --> 46:52.530
Do you know any of my friends?

46:52.740 --> 46:53.190
What?

46:53.340 --> 46:55.590
Do you just want to take the clothes or do you want to get changed now?

46:55.730 --> 46:56.710
No, I don't have time.

46:56.850 --> 46:57.730
Just give me the clothes.

46:57.900 --> 46:58.710
No, I wasn't talking to you.

46:59.200 --> 47:00.750
Why are you going to a friend's place at this time?

47:00.910 --> 47:02.080
To study!

47:02.620 --> 47:04.110
Why are you studying at your friend's place?

47:04.500 --> 47:06.590
Why are you nagging me now?

47:06.880 --> 47:09.930
Are you talking back to me? Come over here!

47:10.060 --> 47:10.770
No!

47:11.080 --> 47:12.220
Look at this girl!

47:13.510 --> 47:15.340
What are you doing now? Hurry up and go.

47:53.560 --> 47:56.140
Let me see.

48:32.290 --> 48:34.950
