48:40.490 --> 48:41.730
It's okay, it's okay.

48:42.590 --> 48:44.350
I'll finish it real quick.

48:46.000 --> 48:52.040
It looks like I can't fucking drive the academic bus anymore.

48:54.570 --> 48:56.230
...Things are getting fucking twisted now.

49:02.170 --> 49:06.540
But shit, can't I like you?

49:08.940 --> 49:10.450
I can like you, right?

49:12.370 --> 49:14.040
