52:07.470 --> 52:09.280
I see, you're a cop.

52:16.110 --> 52:18.540
How come the Korean police found me so quickly?

52:20.400 --> 52:22.140
I'm so surprised.

52:26.140 --> 52:29.400
I guess you still don't know who I am now.

52:30.520 --> 52:34.500
