52:36.420 --> 52:38.240
That's that.

53:28.400 --> 53:29.590
You shithead!

53:30.760 --> 53:32.980
Fuck you!

56:59.480 --> 57:01.690
What, what the hell is this guy?

57:03.220 --> 57:07.590
This guy's a fucking psycho.

58:04.610 --> 58:06.490
Fucking asshole.

58:51.710 --> 58:52.480
Hello, sir!

58:52.700 --> 58:57.030
