01:20:19.900 --> 01:20:21.380
Soo-hyun, it's me.

01:20:23.300 --> 01:20:24.590
Soo-hyun.

01:20:25.450 --> 01:20:27.540
Yeah, how are you doing?

01:20:27.600 --> 01:20:29.910
